{"tid":248384,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"《四月是你的謊言》根本無得輸","createTime":"2017-05-18T13:44:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-22T18:34:52.000Z","uid":95584,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3e45605cf62755ebac880c61227d6a15a44366f6","tid":248384,"uid":95584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T13:44:59.000Z","msg":"啱啱見到有條傻閪話《聲之形》係最催淚嘅動漫作品，我心諗你真係戇撚鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無錯《未聞花名》、《你的名字》、《聲之形》的確係好好睇，《你的名字》更加係神作，我仲專登去戲院睇咗兩次，但我真係唔覺得好似啲人吹奏到咁催淚<br />\n<br />\n睇四月睇到最後係真係好心酸、好想標眼淚，事隔兩年到而家聽返《Orange》同睇返宮園薰寫比公生封信都仲好有feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4be1f96c7ac5058181479fa59d12d9faf9c7f1c","tid":248384,"uid":12127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T13:46:04.000Z","msg":"聲之形好撚mk"},{"pid":"34e4e1d9b750394c2c7104f597360ebe9ce70f5d","tid":248384,"uid":95584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T14:01:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聲之形好撚mk</blockquote><br />\n見仁見智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e53c0e23f714036cdbc87d862551bb5958b47d36","tid":248384,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T15:58:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/mHrLeXw.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FmHrLeXw.gif&h=638ef3e4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2f32364cd491e599aeef4c3f83a3c54fa2d46fdf","tid":248384,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T15:59:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/mHrLeXw.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FmHrLeXw.gif&h=638ef3e4&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\